  <div
    class="fb-login-button"
    data-show-faces="true"
    data-width="200"
    data-max-rows="1"
    data-scope="publish_actions">
  </div>

  <div>
  That story will just say that you like a
  <a href="http://www.budgetbytes.com/2011/02/quick-curried-chick-peas/">
  recipe on BudgetBytes</a>. 
  </div>

  <div>
  <input
    type="button"
    value="Post recipe to Facebook"
